	(11,11,X'',X'3C6272202F3E',X'3C6272202F3E',NULL,'\n Theatermuseum\n Museum for Theatre\n The Austrian Museum for Theatre at Palais Lobkowitz was founded in 1991, finally gaining independence from the Austrian National Library, whose theatrical collections from 1922 onwards create the basis for this museum. Its permanent exhibition presents the most beautiful and most interesting of the museum\'s over 1.6 million objects, illustrating the fields of costume design, stage design, photography, posters, sketches, props, and other parts of the world of theatre.','\n Theatermuseum\n Museum for Theatre\n The Austrian Museum for Theatre at Palais Lobkowitz was founded in 1991, finally gaining independence from the Austrian National Library, whose theatrical collections from 1922 onwards create the basis for this museum. Its permanent exhibition presents the most beautiful and most interesting of the museum\'s over 1.6 million objects, illustrating the fields of costume design, stage design, photography, posters, sketches, props, and other parts of the world of theatre.',X'','','',''),
