	(568,749,X'',X'',X'3C6272202F3E',NULL,'\n	Every summer, the Great Garden plays host a large variety of festivals. The \"Festival of Small Arts\" (Kleinkunstfestival) takes place over several days and offers wide range of artistic displays, and the \"Small Festival in the Great Garden\" (Kleines Fest im Großen Garten) has become firmly entrenched as a highlight of the \"Festival Week Herrenhausen\" (Festwochen Herrenhausen). Lastly, the garden is the site of an international fireworks competition which evolved from a local attraction.\n\n	http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Herrenhausen_Gardens\n\n	--------------------------------\n\n	Baroque garden whose history goes back to the year 1666. Criss-crossing its 50 hectares, geometrically precise allées and paths lead to many charming features, such as Germany\'s oldest hedge theatre, built at the end of the 17th century is still in use every summer during the festival weeks','\n	Every summer, the Great Garden plays host a large variety of festivals. The \"Festival of Small Arts\" (Kleinkunstfestival) takes place over several days and offers wide range of artistic displays, and the \"Small Festival in the Great Garden\" (Kleines Fest im Großen Garten) has become firmly entrenched as a highlight of the \"Festival Week Herrenhausen\" (Festwochen Herrenhausen). Lastly, the garden is the site of an international fireworks competition which evolved from a local attraction.\n\n	http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Herrenhausen_Gardens\n\n	--------------------------------\n\n	Baroque garden whose history goes back to the year 1666. Criss-crossing its 50 hectares, geometrically precise allées and paths lead to many charming features, such as Germany\'s oldest hedge theatre, built at the end of the 17th century is still in use every summer during the festival weeks',X'','\n	Every summer, the Great Garden plays host a large variety of festivals. The \"Festival of Small Arts\" (Kleinkunstfestival) takes place over several days and offers wide r